Jacques Tarride https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacques_Tarride 0 Jacques Tarride (10 March 1903 – 5 October 1994) was a French actor. He was the son of the actor Abel Tarride and the brother of the director Jean Tarride. He was born in the 8th arrondissement of Paris and died in La Loupe, Eure-et-Loir.
